official_title: A bill to designate the Federal plaza located between the Twin Towers of the Oakland Federal Building in Oakland, California, as the "Donald P. McCullum Memorial Plaza."

summary.text: Designates the Federal plaza located between the Twin Towers of the Oakland Federal Building in Oakland, California, as the Donald P. McCullum Memorial Plaza.
